{"tid":2434062,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"中原城市領先指數按星期升0.34%　連升兩周","createTime":"2021-03-05T09:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T19:38:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68819f136768ed4add76df8c745152f954718fdc","tid":2434062,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578953-20210305.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578953-20210305.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=dc7a0514\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578953-20210305.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=35521026\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578953-20210305.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n反映本港二手樓價走勢的中原城市領先指數(CCL)最新報177.17，按星期升0.34%，連升兩星期。<br />\n<br />\n中原表示，樓價走勢反覆上升，新春前買家入市，樓價升勢由大型屋苑主導。而4大整體指數本周齊升，中小型單位升0.31%，大型單位亦反彈0.48%。<br />\n<br />\n分區樓價個別發展，九龍及港島分別按星期升1.24%及0.82%，新界東則跌0.77%，新界西亦跌0.93%。"},{"pid":"cf22c09326fa02aad8ce863eb2f0e4c8b1af9837","tid":2434062,"uid":149494,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"時事台不會告訴你的事"},{"pid":"8699ea5daa8744280dc42e4e6d1dc5a22bd79deb","tid":2434062,"uid":96481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf22c09326fa02aad8ce863eb2f0e4c8b1af9837","tid":2434062,"uid":149494,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"時事台不會告訴你的事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa4ccba1af4f966bfc3e9f5fc735b2e84096141","tid":2434062,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf22c